AddressInfo.Title: E-Bike Charging Station ‘George-Bähr-Str. 14’
AddressInfo.AccessComments: Sockets are located on the green strip to the right at one of the central light blue basement windows (the one under the signs ‘Einfahrt freihalten!’ und ‘Feuerwehrzufahrt’) in the driveway of the yellow multi-family house with the address: George-Bähr-Straße 14, 01069 Dresden. The white socket distributor either hangs out or lies protected on top of the tilted window. Don't forget to switch it on with the small switch on the side (white LED in front must light up)!

Connections.Comments: 2x Schuko (Type F, CEE 7/3; 230V/16A), 2x USB-A (5V/2.4A) and 1x USB-C (5V/3A) (USB-A + USB-C max. 3.4A). On request, I can provide multiple Shimano Steps chargers (EC-E8004 42V/4.6A, EC-E6000 42V/4.0A, EC-E6002 42V/1.8A), USB-C PD chargers (up to 100W) and all kinds of USB cables as well as repair material for camping equipment (Seam Grip sealant and adhesive, sleeping pad and tent patches etc.), bike tools, an air pump, gas cartridges (screw-on Primus-type and bayonet Campingaz-type) and maybe a spare part or two for your bike. Please feel free to let us also know if you need to fill up some drinking water or use the restroom!

GeneralComments: Bicycles/e-bikes only. If you have any questions, please call us at +49 1512 2862747 or send us a message (preferred) via SMS/Threema/Telegram/Signal/WhatsApp (24/7). We are also very happy about a short note that you are charging or planning to charge! :) If a neighbour asks, refer to family ‘Jahn/Strätz’. Free WiFi available without registration (‘Freifunk’). Free WCs also available in numerous public university buildings on the other side of the street (e.g. Zeuner-Bau, 30 m). Restaurants/cafés/supermarkets/drugstore/pharmacy nearby: Dersim (200 m), Bäckerei Möbius (250 m), Grill Cube (350 m), NP1/Edeka/dm/Netto/Helmholtz-Apotheke (350 m), Rewe (500 m), Konsum (600 m). Bicycles can be locked directly to the window grille. Have a good ride!
